snippet.title: Need for Speed Shift iPhone
snippet.description:
http://www.eagames.co.uk/game/need-for-speed-shift-iphone#1

Race up to 20 awesome cars on your iPhone and iPod touch. View the track from the detailed in-car cockpit and 3 other angles. Take on the world's top pros, and earn rewards for your Aggressiveness, Precision, and Style on 18 tracks in 3 international locations.
